<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Taska - Task Management</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #4f46e5;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            color: #4f46e5;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .logo-subtitle {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .welcome-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #6366f1 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .welcome-box h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 22px;
        }
        .feature-box {
            background-color: #f8f9ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #4f46e5;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .feature-box h4 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #4f46e5;
        }
        .feature-box ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .feature-box li {
            margin: 8px 0;
            color: #555;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #4f46e5;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #4338ca;
        }
        .role-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #e0e7ff;
            color: #4f46e5;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">✓ Taska</div>
            <div class="logo-subtitle">Smart Task Management Platform</div>
        </div>

        <p>Hello <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong>,</p>

        <div class="welcome-box">
            <h3>🎉 Welcome to Taska!</h3>
            <p>Your account is ready. Let's start organizing your tasks and boosting your productivity!</p>
        </div>

        <p>Your account has been successfully created as a <span class="role-badge">{{role}}</span></p>

        <div class="feature-box">
            <h4>🚀 What You Can Do With Taska:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>📋 Create and organize tasks with priorities</li>
                <li>📅 Set due dates and track deadlines</li>
                <li>✓ Mark tasks complete and build streaks</li>
                <li>🏆 Earn badges for consistency</li>
                <li>👥 Collaborate with team members</li>
                <li>📊 View task analytics and progress</li>
                <li>🔔 Get smart reminders for upcoming tasks</li>
                <li>💾 Access your tasks from any device</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="https://taska-rho.vercel.app/" class="btn">Launch Taska</a>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-box">
            <h4>🎯 Getting Started:</h4>
            <ol style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Complete your profile</li>
                <li>Create your first task</li>
                <li>Set your task preferences</li>
                <li>Start building productive habits</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-box">
            <h4>✨ Pro Tips:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>🔥 Build streaks by completing tasks daily</li>
                <li>📍 Use categories to organize by project</li>
                <li>⏰ Set reminders for important tasks</li>
                <li>🤝 Invite team members to collaborate</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 25px;">
            <strong>Questions?</strong> Our support team is here to help!
        </p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing Taska - where productivity meets simplicity!</p>
            <p>&copy; 2026 Taska. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>🚀 Made to help you accomplish more</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 